  Npc_GerudoDesert001_Defeat_001:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 已經回到
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 格魯德小鎮
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "囉。\n不過看來起來非常疲累……\n畢竟進行了那麼激烈的戰鬥，\n這也是正常的吧……"
  Npc_GerudoDesert001_Finish_001:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "雖然還不知道\n接下來會發生什麼事，\n但沒想到真的\n讓神獸平靜下來了呢……"
  Npc_GerudoDesert001_Invasion_001:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "人就在上面。\n\n雖然之前非常疲累，\n現在已經完全恢復精神了。\n她小小的身體卻要背負這麼沉重的負擔……\n我卻什麼忙都幫不上，真是懊惱……"
  Npc_GerudoDesert001_Strategy_001:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "真沒想到……\n\n來的會是\n你這種小不點……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n你真的敢和"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 神獸
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "戰鬥嗎……？\n\n不過……"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "這麼認同你，\n肯定有什麼原因吧。\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 就在這間
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所的頂端
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "等著，\n快點上去吧。"
  Npc_GerudoDesert001_Strategy_002:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 就在
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 上面
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "等著，\n別讓她等太久喔。"
  Npc_oasis003_Defeat_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 24
      - text: 說不定……這是第一次……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n第一次本宮靠著自己的力量，\n盡到身為族長的責任……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "接下來就拜託你了，\n現在只有你能鎮壓它了。\n不過……你要答應本宮，\n一定要平安地回來……"
  Npc_oasis003_Finish_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 11
      - text: 哦哦！你回來了啊！？
  Npc_oasis003_Finish_003:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 18
      - text: 你沒事真是太好了……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 1
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 80
      - text: 真是太好了……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
  Npc_oasis003_Finish_004:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 鎮壓
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 娜波力斯
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "後，巨大的沙塵暴也已平息……\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 大災厄
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的動向雖仍令人掛心……\n不過至少人民不必\n再為"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 娜波力斯
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 而煩惱了……
  Npc_oasis003_Finish_005:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 這是過去
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 烏爾波扎大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "曾使用過的\n我們格魯德一族的珍貴武具。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 9
      - text: 既然你是
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 烏爾波扎大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的朋友，\n那送給你是再好不過了。"
  Npc_oasis003_Finish_009:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 0
      - text: 這是感謝你幫忙的謝禮。
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 神器
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "被偷走一事……\n真是本國有史以來絕無僅有的失態……\n我無顏去見\n烏爾波扎大人和列祖列宗……\n人民應該也切身體會到\n年幼君王的無能了吧……"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_002:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "不是這樣的！\n\n神器會被偷，\n都是因為我等護衛的失職！\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 1
      - text: 要是我當初更加警戒的話……
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_003:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 辛苦妳了，碧優拉……
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_101:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "如你所見，本宮還只是個孩子。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "雖然人民都用溫暖的眼神關愛著本宮，\n但這對本宮而言，有時也是一種痛苦……\n本宮一直逞強，期盼能早日發揮族長的能力，\n得到人民真正的認同。\n但卻發生了神器被偷的事件，\n當時真的覺得一切都完了……"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_102:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 如……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "如何？\n適合我嗎？"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 33
            - 34
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 2
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_103:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 80
      - text: ……如、如何？
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_104:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 9
      - text: "呵呵……不知為何……\n明明開戰在即，\n你的一句話，\n卻讓本宮感到安心不已……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "本宮這就先行出發，\n我們在小鎮"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 東南方
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 的
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 會合吧。
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_105:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 1
      - text: ……是、是嗎？
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_106:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - text: 關於
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 神獸瓦‧娜波力斯
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "徘徊的地點，\n在搜尋神器的期間出現大幅變化。"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_107:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "本宮會和心愛的沙海象\n帕特麗夏一起等你的。"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_108:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 要接近
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 娜波力斯
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ，得駕著
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 沙海象
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "才到得了。\n\n剛好"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "離小鎮不算太遠，\n你駕著"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 沙海象
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 過來，順便練習一下吧。
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_109:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 9
      - text: "本宮等你很久囉……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "呵呵……你不必多言……\n\n本宮可是格魯德的族長，\n當然能感應到你身上散發出來的神器之力。"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_111:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: "就算是英傑，\n也需要時間做心理準備是嗎……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n那本宮就先行出發。\n\n若你下定決心，\n就來小鎮"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 東南方
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 的
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 找本宮吧。
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_112:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "說不定將來會給小鎮帶來危險。\n\n本宮作為族長……作為格魯德的一員……\n無論如何都要阻止它才行，\n你願意一起來嗎？"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 122
            - 123
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_113:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 16
      - text: 話說……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n果然很大啊……"
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_114:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: ……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: ……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_115:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: ……是、是喔。
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_117:
    attributes: Npc_oasis051
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 19
      - text: "怎麼了？\n幹嘛愣在那？"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n比起這個……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  Npc_oasis003_GetBack_118:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "就在這種困境之中，你出現了。\n這肯定是烏爾波扎大人的指引吧……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 好了……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: 將頭盔交給本宮吧……
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "要是那時你沒撤退的話，\n本宮說不定早已被打倒了……\n不過本宮已經不要緊了。\n\n你怎麼樣？\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 炸彈箭
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 和
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 弓
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 準備好了嗎？
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_002:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: "若不能同心協力，\n是無法鎮壓它的……\n本宮會在這裡等待，\n直到你準備好為止。"
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_003:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: "平安生還比什麼都還重要，\n在你理解之前，說明幾次都行。"
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_004:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 首先要駕著
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 沙海象
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "接近它，\n本宮負責帶路，\n而你就找出空隙，\n用"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 炸彈箭攻擊
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "它的四隻腳，\n娜波力斯是靠大地之力驅動的，\n只要攻擊腳部，一定就能讓它停下來。\n但是……\n\n它所釋放的落雷非常兇險，\n被打到一次就會造成致命傷……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 有了這個
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 雷鳴頭盔
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "就能抵擋落雷，\n能夠保護你不被落雷攻擊。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 17
      - text: "但……頭盔的力量無法護及遠處……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "若離本宮太遠，\n就無法保護你不被落雷攻擊，\n千萬要記得這點。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "還有……\n\n你要答應本宮，若是受傷過重，\n難以繼續戰鬥，就"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 撤退到這間監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n絕對不要勉強自己。\n\n這是最終確認……\n\n你下定決心了嗎？"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 110
            - 111
            - 112
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 2
          unknown: 8
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_005:
    attributes: Npc_oasis003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 那就出發吧！！
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_006:
    attributes: Npc_oasis033
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "要是繼續拉開距離的話，\n會跟丟"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 娜波力斯
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 的！？
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_007:
    attributes: Npc_oasis033
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 19
      - text: 要先折返嗎？
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 113
            - 114
          selected_index: 1
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis003_Invasion_008:
