      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "我會自己想辦法，\n你也快點逃走吧！"
  Npc_oasis004_GetBack_Near_001:
    attributes: Npc_GerudoDesert004
    contents:
      - text: 不想想辦法逃走的話。
  Npc_oasis007_Defeat_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 我一直擔心
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "會有什麼閃失，\n感到坐立難安……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "但看來這些擔心似乎是多餘的。\n\n不知不覺間，"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n也成長為名副其實的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 族長大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 了……
  Npc_oasis007_Finish_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 35
      - text: "真的很感謝你的壯舉……\n\n要是有我們能幫上忙的地方，\n不要客氣盡管說喔。"
  Npc_oasis007_GetBack_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "怎麼了？\n\n對英傑而言，\n找回神器這種小事，應該輕而易舉吧。"
  Npc_oasis007_GetBack_002:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "若要詢問盜賊的事，\n你可以先去找"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 琪珂隊長
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "了解一下，\n走下那邊的樓梯就能找到她了。"
  Npc_oasis007_GetBack_003:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 6
            - 9
      - text: "就展露一下\n你的身手吧。"
  Npc_oasis007_GetBack_101:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 在
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 2樓
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n\n居然讓你這種人\n出入寢宮……\n真不知"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "是怎麼想的……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "聽好了！\n\n要是"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "有什麼閃失，\n我可不會放過你！"
  Npc_oasis007_Strategy_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "從一開始\n就已經知道你的事了吧……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 虧我還以為自己很有看人的眼光，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 沒想到我還是太嫩了啊……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n好了，宮殿的守衛就交給我，\n你趕快去"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "吧。\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 1
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 就拜託你了……
  Npc_oasis007_Strategy_003:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "沒想到你真的幫我們拿回頭盔了……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 18
      - text: "請原諒我多次失禮……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "為了守護國家……守護露珠大人，\n我不斷磨練槍術至今，\n但卻無能與"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 神獸
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "戰鬥……\n現在只能依靠你了。\n快，你趕快去"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 監視所
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "吧！\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 就拜託你了……
  Npc_oasis024_Ready_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis024
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound2
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 205
      - text: "有伯伊！有伯伊啊！\n快抓住他！！"
  Npc_oasis024_Ready_005:
    attributes: Npc_oasis024
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "伯伊不得進入小鎮，\n這是格魯德的規定。\n明白了嗎！？\n不准再來這裡！"
  Npc_oasis024_Ready_006:
    attributes: Npc_oasis024
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "又是你啊……\n\n我已經說過了，\n伯伊不得進入小鎮！\n明白了嗎！？\n下次不准再來這裡！"
  Npc_oasis024_Ready_007:
    attributes: Npc_oasis024
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: "你這傢伙……\n還真是學不乖啊，一而再、再而三地……\n我已經說過了，格魯德的規定就是\n伯伊不得進入小鎮！\n你這輩子\n都不准再來這裡！！"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_001:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "雖然隊長說了要我們協助你，\n但現在知道的就只有這些而已。"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 30
            - 31
            - 32
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 2
          unknown: 8
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_004:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "盜賊是自稱依蓋隊的一群高手，\n善於變裝，擁有高超的隱匿技術。\n這次事件也是趁著黑夜潛入宮中，\n偷取"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 神器
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "後，如煙一般地消失無蹤。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "據說他們是希卡族的後裔，\n從前被王族驅逐後，轉而投靠惡勢力。\n但話說回來，為何要偷"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 雷鳴頭盔
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ……
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_005:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "雖然已經查明盜賊的\n基地就在"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 卡爾薩谷
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n但山谷的道路非常險峻……\n\n我曾駕著"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 沙海象
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n多次嘗試闖入，\n但都未能深入其中。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: "一想到在沙漠中輸給其他部族，\n就感到羞愧無比……"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 30
            - 32
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_006:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "雖然已經日以繼夜地調查……\n但現在知道的就只有這些而已。"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 30
            - 31
            - 32
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 2
          unknown: 8
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_007:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "要是不知道基地位置，\n可以去問"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 西北門的守衛
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 西北門
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "就在這個兵營出去的左手邊。\n\n本來應該要幫你帶路的，\n但我這邊也遇上一堆麻煩……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 真是的……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n到底該從哪開始著手……"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_008:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "盜賊是自稱依蓋隊的一群高手，\n善於變裝，擁有高超的隱匿技術。\n這次事件也是趁著黑夜潛入宮中，\n偷取"
      - control:
