      - text: "一想到在沙漠中輸給其他部族，\n真是感到羞愧無比……"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_201:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 19
      - text: "喂，有沒有看到芭樂塔？\n那傢伙跑去哪了？"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_202:
    attributes: Npc_oasis040
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "芭樂塔她說要去窺探盜賊的基地……\n然後就一鼓作氣跑出去了！\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 16
      - text: "但是……怪了，\n她已經兩天沒回來了……"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_203:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 20
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - text: 笨、笨、
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 笨蛋……！！
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "為什麼要讓她單獨行動……！\n而且，都兩天了還沒報告！！"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_204:
    attributes: Npc_oasis040
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 4
      - text: "非、非常抱歉……\n我以為她只是去看一下就會回來……\n心想應該沒問題的……"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_205:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 16
      - text: 可惡啊……不僅要尋找
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 神器
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的下落，\n現在還多了個"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 芭樂塔
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "要找……！\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: "這樣的失職要是傳到隊長耳裡，\n肯定逃不了繞格魯德沙漠100圈的責罰……！"
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_206:
    attributes: Npc_oasis041
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 那個……我們該怎麼辦……？
  Npc_oasis042_GetBack_207:
    attributes: Npc_oasis042
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: 我現在正在想啊！！
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
  talk00:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: 這是格魯德族族長
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 露珠大人
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的跟前！\n有事的話，就在那邊稟告吧！"
  talk01:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 0
      - text: 妳說想進入娜波力斯？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n有能力駕馭的\n只有和烏爾波扎大人一樣被稱為英傑的人物，\n但她們都在100年前的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 大災厄
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "中\n喪失了性命。\n妳到底在說什麼蠢話……"
  talk02:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 14
      - text: 難道你這傢伙是伯伊……
  talk04:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "但是……\n我們還沒弄清楚那位的來歷，\n若就這樣將這重大任務交給他，\n這實在是……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  talk05:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "關於偷走神器的盜賊，\n士兵們知道詳細的情況。"
  talk06:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 但……但是，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n據說海利亞的英傑\n帶著一把"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 傳說之劍
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n但這位身上看起來\n似乎並沒有那種東西……"
  talk07:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 你先去那邊的兵營，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n找"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 琪珂隊長
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 問問吧。
  talk08:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 16
      - text: "不過如此一來……當初的英傑中\n應該沒有海利亞人的芭伊才對……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  talk13:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "不必擔心，\n若真的是傳說中的英傑，\n找回頭盔也不是件難事吧。"
  talk15:
    attributes: Npc_oasis007
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "……那先這樣如何？\n先請那位幫我們找回頭盔……"
